'''Link''' is an [[interbank network]] in Indonesia. It connects four [[state owned]] banks. The banks are  [[Bank Mandiri]], [[Bank Tabungan Negara]], [[Bank Negara Indonesia|BNI 46]], and [[Bank Rakyat Indonesia]]. This network is owned by State-owned Banks Association (HIMBARA). This network provides cash withdrawal and inquiry services in their network.

